# Pre-push intentionally runs no checks.
#
# It used to run `pnpm test:coverage` — a full instrumented suite that also enforces
# the coverage threshold from vitest.config.ts. That run takes minutes and repeatedly
# stalled or aborted pushes, so it has been removed from the push path.
#
# Run the coverage gate manually when you want it (e.g. before a release):
#
#   pnpm test:coverage      # also part of `pnpm lint:health`
#
# The plain `pnpm test` suite still runs in CI (.github/workflows/ci.yml).
